   &UR; SREBRENICA: `CLEANSED' OF MUSLIMS, BUT NOT OF SERB HATRED &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; SREBRENICA-SCARS-INDEPENDENT &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   SREBRENICA, BOSNIA _ ``I will never forget this place,'' said
Tima Mehmedovic, trembling on the verge of hysteria. ``It was where
I saw my husband for the last time.'' Mrs. Mehmedovic, 47, came
Tuesday _ along with nearly 3,000 other Bosnian Muslims, mostly
women _ to a wrecked battery factory on the outskirts of Srebrenica
to mark the fifth anniversary of the worst war crime in Europe
since the Nazi era, and the worst humiliation that United Nations
peacekeepers have suffered....By Raymond Whitaker, The Independent &QL;
