<P>
   3. ALLISON FISHER IS THE TIGER WOODS OF NINE-BALL, by Joseph
Nocera
</P>
<P>
   Nine-ball has become the default billiards game in both the
men's and women's professional circuits. And at the Woman's
National Championship, Allison Fisher is the Tiger Woods, the
Michael Jordan, the Wayne Gretzky, of nine-ball. Like them, she
makes the impossible look easy, and the difficult routine. Maybe
it's time for The Nine-Ball Battle of the Sexes.
</P>
