<TEXT>
<P>
   BLACKS, HISPANICS LACKING AT TOP OF TECH PYRAMID IN 1999
</P>
<P>
   ....................................................................
Silicon Valley
</P>
<P>
   ...................................U.S.
Population...........Tech Executives (1)
</P>
<P>
   White Non-Hispanic.............72 %.......................89 %
</P>
<P>
   Black.................................12
