<SLUG> BC-SITE-OF-WEEK-LADN </SLUG>
  
(For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Eds: Weekly Web site box) 
By DAVID BLOOM 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL; 
SITE OF THE WEEK &QL; 
