   (NYT13) EL SALADO, Colombia -- July 13, 2000 --
COLOMBIA-MILITARY-2 -- Pieces of tables and chairs used by members of
a death squad remain scattered on a basketball court where residents
of El Salado were summoned, judged and executed. During three days in
